Apply correlation filtering and impute missing values

Source: R/tidyMS_R6_workflowFunctions.R
workflow_corr_filter_impute.Rd

Apply correlation filtering and impute missing values

workflow_corr_filter_impute(pdata, config, minCorrelation = 0.6)

Arguments

pdata

data.frame

config

AnalysisConfiguration

minCorrelation

correlation threshold default 0.7

See also

Other workflows: INTERNAL_FUNCTIONS_BY_FAMILY, workflow_DIA_NA_preprocessing(), workflow_correlation_preprocessing_protein_intensities()

Examples



bb <- prolfqua_data('data_ionstar')$filtered()
#> Column added : nr_peptide_Id_IN_protein_Id
bb$config <- old2new(bb$config)
stopifnot(nrow(bb$data) == 25780)
config <- bb$config$clone(deep=TRUE)
data <- bb$data
data$nr_peptide_Id_IN_protein_Id <- NULL

config$parameter$min_nr_of_notNA  <- 3
res <- workflow_corr_filter_impute(data,config)
